{"tid":2054294,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇大埔既朋友入黎，真係水浸到閪咁？","createTime":"2020-06-07T05:05:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-07T06:27:17.000Z","uid":213877,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ba584b5cdfcd6664c732fa08a7124529af58edf9","tid":2054294,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T05:05:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4631216/org/79ffa3e04d4cbbe3dd529e8e11072ce0.png/VzdxPQ3ACh-srAoqE9MWWgkHz8_Xy8_UmodzWZqHc1k?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4631216%2Forg%2F79ffa3e04d4cbbe3dd529e8e11072ce0.png%2FVzdxPQ3ACh-srAoqE9MWWgkHz8_Xy8_UmodzWZqHc1k%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=8a81fb60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4631219/org/10487d87fab434fb34511f86dae95eee.jpg/U5xG3ae8oyzF_EIQsmCsLxeF6RSjgbNqGY16RRmNekU?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4631219%2Forg%2F10487d87fab434fb34511f86dae95eee.jpg%2FU5xG3ae8oyzF_EIQsmCsLxeF6RSjgbNqGY16RRmNekU%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=dcead139&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本港連日下雨，今早更加雷雨交加，新界多區發生水浸，天文台先後發出「黃色暴雨警告信號」及「紅色暴雨警告信號」。新界多區民居遭洪水淹浸、部份道路山泥傾瀉要全線封鎖，有小巴在水中死火，大埔碗窰疑因大雨，導致河水泛濫，洪水不斷拍打及沖上河邊圍欄。而大埔、北區及大嶼山至少有33名居民一度被困，需要消防救援。翻查今日天文台發出的天氣稿及雨量數據，原來黃雨、紅雨生效期間，大埔區及離島區的降雨量最高錄得80至108毫米雨量，早已達到甚至超越黑雨的水平。"},{"pid":"36ff981e759d2e9b1f62d2fa4a1e402cc4790688","tid":2054294,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T05:24:49.000Z","msg":"低窪"},{"pid":"e1c37502c649776c726e931a7cc0dea1f7b93549","tid":2054294,"uid":203799,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T05:27:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/06/07/132730_4c25b026f7e5a74a7b8ff4ab81c24d56.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F06%2F07%2F132730_4c25b026f7e5a74a7b8ff4ab81c24d56.png&h=8fd5f878&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca2cb60bcd5422aee31b95cbb6f54e3135bed250","tid":2054294,"uid":203799,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e1c37502c649776c726e931a7cc0dea1f7b93549","tid":2054294,"uid":203799,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T05:27:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/06/07/132730_4c25b026f7e5a74a7b8ff4ab81c24d56.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F06%2F07%2F132730_4c25b026f7e5a74a7b8ff4ab81c24d56.png&h=8fd5f878&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T05:29:21.000Z","msg":"Btw 個到部𨋢次次落雨都實壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n起黎浸壞"},{"pid":"306d14e0da8f3cc7657faded014edcc1ec2ae1a9","tid":2054294,"uid":228337,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T06:27:17.000Z","msg":"唔敢話正常<br />\n<br />\n不過係落大雨常見現象"}]}